law.text: There shall be paid to the board by each applicant at the time of his application for a license, a nonrefundable fee not to exceed four hundred dollars ($400).
law.history: Amended 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 126, sec. 6, effective June 24, 2003. -- Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 252, sec. 5, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 8, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 359, sec. 10, effective June 19, 1976. -- Created 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 9, effective June 14, 1962.
